= Complex Nesting

Complex nesting demonstrates how different elements can be nested together.

== Nested Lists

== Unordered List with Nested Ordered List

* First unordered item

  . First ordered sub-item
  . Second ordered sub-item

* Second unordered item

  . Another ordered sub-item
  . Yet another ordered sub-item

== Ordered List with Nested Unordered List

. First ordered item

  * Unordered sub-item
  * Another unordered sub-item

. Second ordered item

  * More unordered items
  * And another

